    "This dataset was chosen for its comprehensive coverage of topics and its ability to challenge the model across different dimensions of knowledge, reasoning, and understanding.",
    "Table 1 summarizes the main features of the BIG-Bench dataset.",
    "The training process involved initial training on the BIG-Bench dataset to establish a baseline performance level, followed by fine-tuning with a subset of tasks specifically selected to improve factual accuracy and reduce hallucination.",
    "The integration with the Google Query API was also tested during training, with scenarios designed to simulate real-world use cases where the model would need to query for information.",
    "This approach allowed for the refinement of the integration mechanism and the optimization of the model's performance in leveraging external data sources.As indicated in Table 1, the BIG-Bench dataset provides a robust framework for evaluating and enhancing the capabilities of language models like Llama 2 7b, especially in terms of addressing challenges like factual accuracy and hallucination."
